Você o quê?

180
00:14:05,757 --> 00:14:07,426
<i>Se o passado deles mudou,</i>

181
00:14:15,116 --> 00:14:16,416
<i>o meu também?</i>

182
00:14:18,130 --> 00:14:19,430
