183
00:14:21,582 --> 00:14:22,882
A janela.

184
00:14:23,927 --> 00:14:25,229
Que janela?

185
00:14:45,705 --> 00:14:47,005
Elliot?

186
00:14:48,154 --> 00:14:49,489
O que você tem?

187
00:14:49,906 --> 00:14:51,206
<i>Cadê meu quarto?</i>

188
00:14:53,597 --> 00:14:54,897
Era bem aqui.

189
00:14:55,704 --> 00:14:57,004
Você está bem?

190
